Revision history for MiniPAN

0.04    2009-11-11 03:50
    - moved to Module::Install
    - use http cpan mirror instead of ftp which is less painfull usually
    - added dependenciy to external binaries (make, sudo)
    - install minipan script properly into $PATH
    - added support for Makefile.PL that doesnt support --skipdeps
      (like WWW::Mechanize apparently)

0.03    2009-01-09 03:15
    - minor fixes

0.02    2009-01-09 00:28
    - use perl modules instead of system() for downloading and extracting
	  sources
    - therefore added following dependencies:
	  * LWP::UserAgent
	  * IO::Uncompress::Gunzip
	  * Archive::Tar
	  * File::Path

0.01    2009-01-03 22:01
    - First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
